Did an earbud purchase from NBC Today Show Steals and Deals.  Product took a month but I understand.

One earbud never worked. The other my wife didn't want. I asked for a refund authorization.

First I was told to contact the store where I purchased. The items came directly from the NJ office.
Then I was told to cony the Today Show.  They do not seem to stand behind their products.

We out our money.
